message.content: "Hardly likely, my sweet. Luke's surgery goes on for hours. If they get in before eight-thirty, even though they're standing on one another's toes, I've got to see 'em. If I am free, though, I'll give you a ring - O.K.?" O.K., she had replied readily. So how could Nigel have been at the Loads of Trouble roadhouse, dancing with a blonde at eight-thirty that very evening?
